.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-CAPACITY-CHECK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-capacity-check \- list channels with local balance below a threshold
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-capacity-check
.I min_sat
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns all
.B CHANNELD_NORMAL
channels whose local balance (in satoshis) is below
.IR min_sat .
Useful for spotting depleted outbound capacity before sending.
Returns an empty array if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{channel_id, peer_id, to_us_msat, total_msat}]
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-balance (1),
.BR lightning-liquidity-report (1)
